  "body": "In communities, with 0.3.0-beta, after restart (signout/signin) the wrong number of pinned messages is shown. Moreover this number evolves if scrolling the community, number can still be bad after scrolling though. Moreover this number can be more than the limit 3 pinned messages. \r\n\r\nThis is reproductible 100% of the times.\r\n\r\nExemple:\r\n- yesterday I created 4 messages m1-m2-m3-m4 then I pinned m1-m2-m3, and then pinned m4\r\n- this morning after restart of status desktop, the indicator shows 1 pinned message only (which seems empty when clicking on the pin). If I scroll, then 4 pinned messages are shown and one is empty\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11461437/133437258-27c8f756-3214-46c9-b053-515fa63e51c7.mov\r\n\r\n",
